  "content": "Collaboration security\nCollaboration security is a framework of tools and practices designed to protect the exchange of information and workflows within digital workspaces like messaging apps, shared documents, and video conferencing platforms. It aims to safeguard against unauthorized access, data leaks, and cyber threats while enabling seamless collaboration among team members. Effective collaboration security ensures that employees can work together securely from anywhere, maintaining compliance and protecting sensitive information.",
